== 發行 ==
2015年4月，宣布電影定於2016年10月21日在美國上映<ref>{{cite web|url=http://deadline.com/2015/04/ouija-sequel-october-2016-universal-jason-blum-1201418623/|title=‘Ouija 2′ Set For October 2016; Jason Blum Back as Producer - Deadline|first=Denise|last=Petski|work=Deadline|accessdate=August 16, 2015|archive-date=2016-10-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161021134337/http://deadline.com/2015/04/ouija-sequel-october-2016-universal-jason-blum-1201418623/|dead-url=no}}</ref>，而臺灣也於同樣日期上映。

=== 評價 ===
《碟仙：惡靈始源》獲得了正面好評，多數影評人稱讚該片大幅超越了前作，但在觀眾間的評價仍有些兩極。[[爛番茄|爛番茄]]根據105篇評論持有82%的新鮮度，平均得分6.3／10<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/ouija_origin_of_evil |title=Ouija: Origin of Evil (2016) |publisher=Rotten Tomatoes |accessdate=October 20, 2016 |archive-date=2016-10-20 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161020230049/https://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/ouija_origin_of_evil |dead-url=no }}</ref>，這比前集的7%還高出許多。[[Metacritic|Metacritic]]得分65，正評居多<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.metacritic.com/movie/ouija-origin-of-evil|title=Ouija: Origin of Evil reviews|publisher=[[Metacritic|Metacritic]]|accessdate=October 18, 2016|archive-date=2016-10-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161025053215/http://www.metacritic.com/movie/ouija-origin-of-evil|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

=== 票房 ===
該片預計在其首映週末從三千一百六十八間戲院中獲得1600萬美元的票房<ref>{{cite web |url=http://deadline.com/2016/10/the-accountant-ben-affleck-kevin-hart-fall-box-office-ticket-sales-1201835284/ |title=Can Ben Affleck’s ‘The Accountant’ Be An Asset For Weak Fall Box Office? – Preview |work=[[Deadline.com|Deadline.com]] |accessdate=2016-10-21 |archive-date=2016-10-17 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161017193510/http://deadline.com/2016/10/the-accountant-ben-affleck-kevin-hart-fall-box-office-ticket-sales-1201835284/ |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name=budget>{{cite web |url=http://www.latimes.com/entertainment/envelope/cotown/la-et-ct-movie-projector-20161018-snap-story,amp.html |title='Jack Reacher: Never Go Back' to battle 'Ouija' sequel and 'Boo! A Madea Halloween' at box office |work=[[Los_Angels_Times|Los Angels Times]] |accessdate=2016-10-21 |archive-date=2016-10-19 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161019081223/http://www.latimes.com/entertainment/envelope/cotown/la-et-ct-movie-projector-20161018-snap-story,amp.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。美國首映週末票房收入為1406萬美元，位居當週票房排名第三。

